â€¢ **Enhanced Brand Perception:** The client was firmly positioned as a premium artisan, capable of justifying higher price points compared to competitors.

â€¢ **Stronger Customer Loyalty:** The "About the Maker" section and consistent brand storytelling led to more engaged customers and repeat purchases.

